item.title: CVE-2023-41840|2024-10-22T20:54:04.281Z -- fortinet -- forticlientwindows
item.description: A untrusted search path vulnerability in Fortinet FortiClientWindows 7.0.9 allows an attacker to perform a DLL Hijack attack via a malicious OpenSSL engine library in the search path.
